# Semgrep ignore patterns for pan-agent.
#
# Paths listed here are excluded from every semgrep scan (CI, local,
# PostToolUse hook). Only exclude generated/third-party code here —
# first-party source should either be clean or carry an inline
# `// nosemgrep: <rule-id>` suppression with a written justification.

# Embedded Claw3D Next.js bundle — minified, committed artifact from the
# Claw3D frontend build. Scanning generated JS produces a large volume of
# flags (prototype pollution, non-literal regexp, wildcard postMessage)
# that are inherent to bundled/compiled output and unactionable here.
internal/claw3d/bundle/

# Test files — exercise real binaries and simulate HTTP servers by design.
# dangerous-exec-command and no-direct-write-to-responsewriter findings in
# test code are appropriate: exec'ing the binary under test IS the test,
# and simulating an SSE server requires writing raw bytes to a fake
# ResponseWriter.
**/*_test.go

# Platform-specific CGO wrappers for OS APIs. Using unsafe.Pointer to hand
# Go memory to CoreGraphics / User32 / CoreFoundation is the documented
# idiomatic cgo pattern; the alternative is to not use those APIs at all.
# Every use here is local-scope and short-lived (no stored pointers, no
# finalizers) — inspected during 0.4.1 security audit.
internal/tools/keyboard_darwin.go
internal/tools/keyboard_windows.go
internal/tools/mouse_windows.go
internal/tools/window_manager_darwin.go
internal/tools/window_manager_windows.go
internal/claw3d/process_windows.go

# Agent tools whose purpose IS command execution. These are gated by the
# approval.Classify pipeline (internal/approval/classify.go) before they
# run; the CWE-78 / dangerous-exec-command advice "avoid dynamic commands"
# does not apply to a tool whose function is literally to run the command
# the LLM proposed. Tool output never flows to HTML rendering.
internal/tools/code_execution.go
internal/tools/terminal.go

# Go build cache + vendored deps (if ever added).
.gocache/
vendor/

# Frontend build outputs.
desktop/dist/
desktop/src-tauri/target/

# Backup files and OS cruft.
*.orig
*.bak
.DS_Store
